@ic3warm, the WOTLK leveling guides include everything from 1-80.  Blizz has dramatically changed the way we level.  You can now get from 1-60 on one continent (Kalimdor or Eastern Kingdoms) so it includes the new 1-60 guides for each of the continents, your choice of which one.  Of course, the 80-85 stuff isn't available until 12/7 so Zygor will probably have a new guide out then.  This release will get your new Gnome Druid off the ground right...  I'll post new guides as they become available.

@ic3warm, the WOTLK leveling guide files include 1-80.  Of course Cata content will not be released until 12/7 so those guides aren't available yet.  This includes the new quest changes and change of zones due to the Shattering.
